<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 m9 l8 offset-l1">
    <div class="row postit light-green lighten-2">
      <div class="col s5">
        <i class="pin"></i>
        <!-- 포스트를 수정하는 부분 -->
        <div class="fixed-action-btn horizontal" style="top:1em;">
          <a class="btn-floating btn-large">
            <i class="large material-icons yellow darken-1">mode_edit</i>
          </a>
          <ul>
            <li><a class="btn-floating yellow darken-1" href="#"><i class="material-icons">mode_edit</i></a></li>
            <li><a class="btn-floating red" href="#"><i class="material-icons">delete</i></a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- 포스트를 수정하는 부분 -->
        <div class="card-image waves-effect waves-block waves-light">
          <img class="activator" src="/img/mydesk/post/example5.png" height="320em" width="240em">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col s7">
        <h4 style="text-align:center;">리우올림픽!!
          <p><a href="http://www.visualdive.com/2016/07/%ED%98%84%EC%8B%A4%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EB%A7%8C%EB%82%98%EB%8A%94-%ED%94%BC%EC%B9%B4%EC%B8%84-%ED%8F%AC%EC%BC%93%EB%AA%AC%EA%B3%A0-%E7%BE%8E%EC%84%9C-%ED%8F%AD%EB%B0%9C/">리우에서 올림픽이..</a></p>
        </h4>
        <hr>
        <h5 style="text-align:center;">올림픽이 열린다고 한다.</h5>
      </div>
    </div><br>
    <div class="row mypostit light-green lighten-2">
      <div class="col s12">
        <i class="pin"></i>
        <!-- Comment를 수정하는 부분 -->
        <div class="fixed-action-btn horizontal" style="top:1em;">
          <a class="btn-floating">
            <i class="large material-icons yellow darken-1">mode_edit</i>
          </a>
          <ul>
            <li><a class="btn-floating yellow darken-1" href="#"><i class="material-icons">mode_edit</i></a></li>
            <li><a class="btn-floating red" href="#"><i class="material-icons">delete</i></a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Comment를 수정하는 부분 -->
        <h3 style="margin-left:2px; margin-top:2px;"><b>My Idea!</b></h3>
        <div class="text" style="font-size: 25px;">
          피카츄 라이츄 파이리 꼬부기~!
        </div>
        <div class="time">5 min ago</div>
      </div>
    </div><br><hr><br>

    <!-- Comment에 해당하는 부분이 달리는 곳 : mydesk.scss에 해당하는 css값들을 넣어둠-->
    <div class="row commentpostit">
      <div class="chat-body">
        <i class="pin"></i>
        <div class="answer left">
          <div class="avatar">
            <img src="/img/user2.gif" alt="User name" style="width:3em; height:4em;">
            <div class="status offline"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="text">
            Lorem ipsum dolor amet, consectetur adipisicing elit Lorem ipsum dolor amet, consectetur adipisicing elit Lorem ipsum dolor amet, consectetur adiping elit
          </div>
          <div class="time">7 min ago &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="btn-floating red" href="#"><i class="small material-icons">delete</i></a></div>
        </div>
      </div><br>
      <div class="chat-body">
        <div class="answer left">
          <div class="avatar">
            <img src="/img/user3.png" alt="User name" style="width:3em; height:4em;">
            <div class="status offline"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="text">
            wowwowwow 와우와우와우 wowwowwow 오오오오오오 ohohohoh 신기신기하다!
